stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: createPermissionRequest\n（Worker 创建）
    pending --> approved: Leader UI 批准\n（resolvedBy=leader）
    pending --> rejected: Leader UI 拒绝\n（resolvedBy=leader）
    pending --> approved: Worker 自行批准\n（resolvedBy=worker, YOLO/rules）
    approved --> [*]: 文件移入 resolved/\nWorker 继续执行
    rejected --> [*]: 文件移入 resolved/\nWorker 终止工具
